					<h2><a href="https://thethoughtstash.wordpress.com/2015/07/29/dominos-pizza-and-area-of-a-circle/" rel="bookmark">Domino&#8217;s Pizza and the Area of a&nbsp;Circle</a></h2>
				</div>
				<div class="post-4724 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-science-general tag-dominos tag-mathematics tag-pizza">
					<div class="entry">
					<p>My excuse for this post: I&#8217;m between Open University modules at the moment and have spare time on my hands.</p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_4738" style="max-width: 250px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Dominos_pizza_logo.svg"><img data-attachment-id="4738" data-permalink="https://thethoughtstash.wordpress.com/2015/07/29/dominos-pizza-and-area-of-a-circle/dominos_pizza_logo-svg-1/" data-orig-file="https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2015/07/dominos_pizza_logo-svg-1.png?w=500" data-orig-size="240,240" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Domino&#8217;s pizza" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2015/07/dominos_pizza_logo-svg-1.png?w=500?w=240" data-large-file="https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2015/07/dominos_pizza_logo-svg-1.png?w=500?w=240" class="size-full wp-image-4738" src="https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2015/07/dominos_pizza_logo-svg-1.png?w=500" alt="Make nice pizzas, but don't do maths." srcset="https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2015/07/dominos_pizza_logo-svg-1.png 240w, https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2015/07/dominos_pizza_logo-svg-1.png?w=150 150w" sizes="(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px"   /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Make nice pizzas, but don&#8217;t do maths.</p></div>
