<li>A great write-up of Hazel&#8217;s talk by <a href="https://twitter.com/NottsScience">@NottsScience</a>: <a href="http://nottinghamscience.blogspot.co.uk/2014/09/talk-living-on-frack-tured-earth.html">Talk : Living on frack-tured Earth</a>.</li>
</ul>
