			<div class="postwrapper wideposts" id="post-3482">
				<div class="title">
					<small>Posted by: <strong>Kash Farooq</strong> | December 30, 2013 </small>
					<h2><a href="https://thethoughtstash.wordpress.com/2013/12/30/the-pop-sci-book-club-book-6/" rel="bookmark">The Pop Sci Book Club – Book&nbsp;6</a></h2>
				</div>
				<div class="post-3482 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-planetary-science category-popscibookclub tag-mike-brown tag-planetary-science tag-pluto tag-popscibookclub tag-science">
					<div class="entry">
					<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_2902" style="max-width: 510px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img data-attachment-id="2902" data-permalink="https://thethoughtstash.wordpress.com/2013/02/23/the-pop-sci-book-club/popscibookclublogo/" data-orig-file="https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2013/02/popscibookclublogo.jpg?w=500&#038;h=196" data-orig-size="500,196" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="The Pop Sci Book Club" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2013/02/popscibookclublogo.jpg?w=500&#038;h=196?w=300" data-large-file="https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2013/02/popscibookclublogo.jpg?w=500&#038;h=196?w=500" class="size-full wp-image-2902" alt="Psocoptera - an order of insects that are commonly known as booklice." src="https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2013/02/popscibookclublogo.jpg?w=500&#038;h=196" width="500" height="196" srcset="https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2013/02/popscibookclublogo.jpg 500w, https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2013/02/popscibookclublogo.jpg?w=150&amp;h=59 150w, https://thethoughtstash.files.wordpress.com/2013/02/popscibookclublogo.jpg?w=300&amp;h=118 300w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Psocoptera &#8211; an order of insects that are commonly known as booklice.</p></div>
<p>[If you are unsure what this is all about, see <a href="https://thethoughtstash.wordpress.com/2013/02/23/the-pop-sci-book-club/">The Pop Sci Book Club &#8211; an introduction</a>]</p>
<p>PopSciBookClub Book 6 has been selected by <a href="https://twitter.com/MrRegars">Regan Naughton</a>. It is &#8220;<a href="http://www.amazon.co.uk/How-Killed-Pluto-Why-Coming/dp/0385531109">How I Killed Pluto and Why It Had It Coming</a>&#8221; – by Mike Brown (271 pages). So, please <a href="http://www.amazon.co.uk/How-Killed-Pluto-Why-Coming/dp/0385531109">buy the book</a> and join in with the <a href="http://z13.invisionfree.com/Pop_Sci_Book_Club/index.php?act=idx">Pop Sci Book Club forum</a> discussions.</p>
